            <div class="section-content">
                <div class="guidelines-section">
                    <h3 style="color: #2c3e50;">üåç IASP - International Association for the Study of Pain (2024)</h3>
                    <p><strong>Raccomandazioni chiave:</strong></p>
                    <ul style="margin-left: 2rem;">
                        <li>Approccio multimodale per dolore neuropatico cronico</li>
